'''Kathy Oltion''' is a [[science fiction]] [[novelist]] known primarily for her ''[[Star Trek]]'' work, which began with publication in the first two ''[[Star Trek: Strange New Worlds|Strange New Worlds]]'' anthologies from [[Pocket Books]] ("See Spot Run" in the first, "The Quick and the Dead" in the second).
She also co-wrote the novel ''[[The Flaming Arrow|Star Trek: New Earth: The Flaming Arrow]]'' (Book Four of Six) with her husband, [[Jerry Oltion]]. Both authors live in [[Eugene, Oregon]].
In addition to writing science fiction, Kathy Oltion also works in a medical laboratory.
She is a member of the [[Wordos]] writers' group.
